==English==

===Etymology===
From Middle English for "God be with ye(=you)".

===Pronunciation===
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /gUd"baI/
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /gʊd'baj/

===Interjection===
'''goodbye'''
# A [[farewell]], a word said to someone [[leaving]].

===Alternative spellings===
*[[good-bye]]
*[[good-by]]

